name: Shopping Spree
description: Nfts.tips Foundation is a Nonprofit organization that has been supporting the creators, collectors and curators in the nfts space since the beginning of 2021. We asked the community to create a concept and @danny_p3d on instagram created an epic version of the idea. By purchasing this nft, you will be able to build the bank for a shopping spree to happen. Once we get enough tez, we will buy art until our wallet is empty.
